      <title>०४६ उर्वशीशापः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/03_vanaparva/05_indralokAbhigamanaparva/02_svarvRttAntaH/046_urvashIshApaH/</link>
